*Gospodine* je pozvao svoje prijatelje na ručak. (Mr. has invited his friends for lunch.)

On se obratio *gospodinu* pored sebe. (He addressed the gentleman next to him.)

Taj čovek je bio izuzetno uvažen među *gospodinima*. (That man was highly respected among the gentlemen.)

*Gospodinu* je bilo neprijatno da misli na tu stvar. (It was uncomfortable for the gentleman to think about that thing.)

*Gospodin* je izrazio svoje zahvalnosti. (The gentleman expressed his gratitude.)